Embedded fonts
--------------
folea embeds the font files under src/workers/typst-compile/assets/ so Typst notes render
deterministically without network font loading.

- NotoSerif-Regular.ttf
  Family: Noto Serif
  License: SIL Open Font License 1.1
  Source: https://github.com/notofonts/noto-fonts

- LibertinusSerif-Regular.otf
- LibertinusSerif-Bold.otf
- LibertinusSerif-Italic.otf
- LibertinusSerif-BoldItalic.otf
- LibertinusMath-Regular.otf
  Family: Libertinus
  License: SIL Open Font License 1.1
  Source: https://github.com/alerque/libertinus

- NewCM10-Regular.otf
